      • deleteDockingStation

        public boolean deleteDockingStation(DockingStation dockingstation)
        Removes the docking station from the database. If the database does not contain the docking station, it is unchanged If the docking station contains data, the method will change the status of docking station instead of remove it from database.
        Parameters:
        dockingstation - the docking station to be removed from the database, if present.
        Returns:
        true if the database contained the specified docking station. False if the docking station is not existed.
